japanese: 何の話？
english: What about?

japanese: 何の話だ？
english: What about?

japanese: 何よ、突然。/そんな事考えてたの？
english: What, suddenly. /Thinking about that?

japanese: 他校を武力制圧するのが/いいと思います！
english: I think conquering other schools /by force is good!

japanese: 何かあったのか？/世界で一番不幸みたいな顔してよ？
english: Something happen? /You look like the unhappiest person ever?

japanese: 何いってやがる。/まだ一年以上も/高校生活が残ってるだろうが。
english: What are you saying. /You still have over a year /of high school left.

japanese: 何だよ、突然。/そんな事考えてたのか？
english: What, suddenly. /Thinking about that?

japanese: 他の手を考える。じゃあな！
english: I'll think of another way. See ya!

japanese: 体育館に、何しに来てたの？
english: What'd you come to the gym for?

japanese: 何に変わるかわからんが、今の技が/気に入らなければ、やるといいぞ！/どうだ、やってみるか？
english: Don't know what it'll change to, but /if you don't like your move, do it! /Try?

japanese: 何も悩みに限りません。/懺悔や祈りなど、/幅広く受けつけていますよ。
english: Not limited to worries. /Confessions, prayers, /we accept broadly.

japanese: 何も用意してこなかったから、/出せるものがないよ。
english: I didn't bring anything, /so nothing to put out.

japanese: 他のクラスに借りに行く/今ある道具で工夫する/なぐさめる
english: Borrow from other classes/ Work with current tools/ Comfort

japanese: 他の子と行く約束をしてるんだ。
english: I have a promise to go with others.

japanese: 体育館に、何しに来てたんだ？
english: What'd you come to the gym for?

japanese: 何してるの、エッジ！
english: What're you doing, Edge!

japanese: 仮にモデルに転職したとして、/ずっと続けていく自信は、私にはないわ。
english: Even if switching to modeling, /I lack confidence to continue.

japanese: 任せておけ！/僕のオリジナルトレーニングで/お前の必殺技を変えてやろう！
english: Leave it to me! /I'll change your special move /with my original training!

japanese: 何も用意してこなかったから、/出せるものがないなぁ。
english: I didn't bring anything, /so nothing to put out.

japanese: 何マス移動しますか？
english: How many spaces to move?

japanese: 会っても、私と目を合わそうとしないの。/私、２人に何か悪いことしたかな？
english: Even when we meet, they won't look at me. /Did I do something bad?

japanese: 何いってんだよ！/自分のことは自分で決めろよ。/男だろ！
english: What are you saying! /Decide for yourself! /You're a man!

japanese: 何が行われるのか確認もせずにか？/いささか性急で軽率な判断だな。
english: Without confirming what happens? /Rather hasty and rash judgment.

japanese: 何だか、申し訳ないな。/ケガでみんなに迷惑かけた上に、/お祝いまでしてもらうなんて……。
english: Somehow, I'm sorry. /Caused trouble with injury, /and getting congratulations...

japanese: 何、これ？
english: What, this?

japanese: 何だ、これ？
english: What is this?

japanese: 何よ、夏？/急に笑ったりして……。
english: What, Natsu? /Suddenly laughing...

japanese: 何よ、急に……。
english: What, suddenly...

japanese: 何ブツブツいっての、エッジ？
english: What're you muttering, Edge?
